  ## Actions

  > **Note:** This is a 2.x styled addon so it assumes closure actions.
{{/markdown-convert}}

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-3">
    {{ui-button icon='dot-circle-o' size='huge' onClick=(action 'onClick') value='foobar'}}
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-9">
    <span>
      {{#markdown-convert style='github'}}
      The ui-button exposes a single action:

      - `onClick` which returns an object hash with following properties:

          - `button` - the context object for the "ui-button" component (_DOM-less_)
          - `context` - the context object for the contained "ui-button-primitive" component
          - `evt` - the underlying DOM event that was fired
          - `value` - the value of the button that was clicked

      {{/markdown-convert}}
      <br>
      <code>
        \{{ui-button icon='dot-circle-o' size='huge' onClick=(action 'onClick') value='foobar'}}<br>
      </code>
    </span>
  </div>
</div>

